latestPosts.caption:
Feeling truly grateful today. 
A year ago I still remember how nervous I was before starting modeling I was really scared and full of doubts I was afraid to even try But with courage and passion I took the first step and today, after countless shoots, working with amazing people and designers, traveling to new places, and learning so much — I feel proud.
I remember how I used to just think about it, but today, I’m living it. I’m so happy I chose this path and followed my passion.

The journey from doubt to confidence is never easy, but it’s always worth it If you’re scared to start something you love—do it anyway

One year. Many shoots. Endless gratitude.
Grateful for the journey, proud of the growth.

#grateful #faith #proud #explore #foryou #instalike #instamood #instagood #instagram
Strong. Bold. Unapologetic.
